Plans for 0.6.0
===============

  New:
    [ ] Subtitle merge/split (bug #6246)
    [ ] Smarter translation file opening (bug #6245)
    [?] Support .srtx format (bug #6244)

  Changes:
    [D] Copy-paste now works from one project to another


Plans after 0.6.0
=================

  * Wizards (wait for GTK 2.10?)
     - Common error correction
     - Capitalization correction
     - Line reformatting
     - Hearing impaired subtitle removal


